  "title": "Sniffer Tweak",
  "description": "Simple server mod that prevents sniffer eggs from cracking",
  "body": "![Sniffer Tweak Icon](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b319eb8236f7f87b2872c88b34b57637bf2a9c34.png)\n\n## About\n\nThis simple server mod prevents sniffer eggs from hatching when placed in the world, effectively turning them into decorations.\nDue to this change, sniffer eggs can be shapelessly crafted into a sniffer spawn egg which allows the mob to be obtained in survival.\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/sniffer-tweak\"><img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/available/modrinth_vector.svg\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/sniffer-tweak\"><img alt=\"curseforge\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/available/curseforge_vector.svg\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/tnoctua/sniffer-tweak\"><img alt=\"github\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/available/github_vector.svg\"></a>\n\n<img alt=\"forge\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/unsupported/forge_vector.svg\">",
